qMetaDef.title: ADL Overview
qMetaDef.description: Provides a high-level overview of ADL task completion-- the number of incomplete tasks, the average amount of daily minutes, and the percentage of tasks marked as complete using mobile.

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=NUM([# of Ad-Hoc Tasks], '#,##0')&' ad-hoc ??? '&NUM([# Additional Tasks], '#,##0')&' additional'
//&' overdue ??? '&
=NUM([# of Tasks Complete by Mobile], '#,###')&' of '&NUM([# of Tasks], '#,###')&' total tasks'

qProperty.title: Average Additional ADL Minutes per Day

qStringExpression.qExpr: =NUM([# of Tasks Complete by Mobile], '#,##0')&' of '&NUM([# of Tasks Mobile], '#,##0')&' applicable tasks'
=if([% Tasks Completed by Mobile] < .3,'$(purple)', if([% Tasks Completed by Mobile] < .7,'$(orange)', '$(green)'))
='$(value_css)'&'color:'&if([% Tasks Completed by Mobile] < .3,'$(purple)', if([% Tasks Completed by Mobile] < .7,'$(orange)', '$(green)'))
=NUM([# of Tasks Complete by Mobile], '#,###')&' of '&NUM([# of Tasks], '#,###')&' total tasks'

qProperty.title: % Mobile Completion by Community and Resource Role

qStringExpression.qExpr: ='Drills down from division ??? region ??? community ??? resource role.'
='Drills down from division ??? region ??? community ??? resident.'

qDef.qDef: [# of Incomplete Tasks] / [# of Applicable Tasks]

qStringExpression.qExpr: =NUM([# of Incomplete Tasks], '#,##0')&' of '&NUM([# of Applicable Tasks], '#,##0')&' applicable tasks'
=NUM([# of Tasks Complete by Mobile], '#,###')&' of '&NUM([# of Tasks], '#,###')&' total tasks'
